item.description:
Join me for a few hours of Disc golf.

http://www.dgcoursereview.com/reviews.php?id=1588&mode=rev

Basically it's tossing a frisbee into a metal basket. There are 18 holes located on trails thruout the woods. You don't have to be good. Just come out and enjoy the day  with us. I suggest wearing good shoes, bring bug spray , water and a fun attitude. We will meet at the Hillside store across from the park to pick up ourdiscs. There is no charge. We can return there after to have lunch if you'd like.

Questions ??  call Cindy             603-315-0275
